      • buildLogin

        public java.lang.String buildLogin​(com.jalios.jcms.Member guest)
        Description copied from interface: MemberLoginBuilder
        Override this method to define how the login should be built.

        Implementation should return a free login. To check if a login is free, you can use: 

         boolean isFreeLogin = CHANNEL.getMemberFromLogin(login) == null;
        Specified by:
        buildLogin in interface MemberLoginBuilder
        Parameters:
        guest - a wrapper to hold informations about the member to compute its login. (especially, name, firstName, email).

        Implementation should NOT modify the member parameter received.

        Returns:
        the login to use for the given member
        Since:
        csp-6.4
        See Also:
